OL,3,CSurvey reveals how first-time buyers
OL,4,Care achieving dream home on a budget
OL,6,FTwo-thirds (66%) of first-time buyers
OL,7,Fbought a "doer-upper" that needed
OL,8,Frenovation work to save money on the
OL,9,Fproperty price, a survey has found.
OL,11,FNine in 10 (93%) first-time buyers had
OL,12,Fcompleted at least one renovation or
OL,13,FDIY project since moving in,
OL,14,FNationwide Building Society reported.
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@UO]
