OL,3,CSurvey reveals how first-time buyers
OL,4,Care achieving dream home on a budget
OL,6,FOf these, three-quarters (75%) carried
OL,7,Fout more work than they initially
OL,8,Fanticipated, with 25% of these people
OL,9,Fsaying they had done much more than
OL,10,Fexpected and 18% taking on major
OL,11,Fstructural projects to get their
OL,12,Fproperty in order.
OL,14,FBut on the upside, many first-time
OL,15,Fbuyers choosing a "fixer-upper" may be
OL,16,Fable to achieve their dream home at a
OL,17,Freduced cost.
OL,26,@wD@SOUwD@_O]
