OL,3,CSurvey reveals how first-time buyers
OL,4,Care achieving dream home on a budget
OL,6,FMany were able to buy in their
OL,7,Fpreferred location, with 41% saying
OL,8,Fthis was the case, and put their stamp
OL,9,Fon it, with 30% saying they were able
OL,10,Fto shape the home to their tastes over
OL,11,Ftime, the research found.
OL,13,FMore than a fifth (22%) were able to
OL,14,Ffuture-proof their home for plans such
OL,15,Fas starting a family and nearly a
OL,16,Fquarter (23%) also said buying a home
OL,17,Fthat needed renovation work helped
OL,18,Fthem to increase the value of their
OL,19,Fproperty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
