OL,3,CSurvey reveals how first-time buyers
OL,4,Care achieving dream home on a budget
OL,6,FAnd 89% of first-time buyers described
OL,7,Fthemselves as confident, excited or
OL,8,Fwilling to take on DIY.
OL,10,FA fifth (20%) of first-time buyers
OL,11,Fsaid they chose a property that needed
OL,12,Fwork doing to it because they enjoy
OL,13,Fdoing DIY and renovation projects.
OL,15,FSix in 10 (60%) first-time buyers have
OL,16,Fspent more than #2,500 on DIY and home
OL,17,Fimprovement projects since moving in,
OL,18,Fwith 29% spending more than #5,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
