OL,3,CSurvey reveals how first-time buyers
OL,4,Care achieving dream home on a budget
OL,6,FThe most common projects include
OL,7,Fpainting and decorating, kitchen and
OL,8,Fbathroom improvements, new flooring
OL,9,Fand general repairs. Nearly a fifth
OL,10,F(18%) have taken on bigger structural
OL,11,Fprojects, such as knocking through
OL,12,Fwalls, building extensions or
OL,13,Fconverting lofts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
