OL,3,CSurvey reveals how first-time buyers
OL,4,Care achieving dream home on a budget
OL,6,FNationwide said its research indicates
OL,7,Fthat a loft conversion or extension
OL,8,Fwith a large double bedroom and
OL,9,Fbathroom can increase the value of a
OL,10,Ftypical three-bedroom home by up to
OL,11,F24%. Any net financial gains or losses
OL,12,Ffrom home improvements will depend on
OL,13,Findividual circumstances.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
