PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778292208
OL,3,CSurvey reveals how first-time buyers
OL,4,Care achieving dream home on a budget
OL,6,FNearly two-thirds (62%) of first-time
OL,7,Fbuyers factored DIY or renovation
OL,8,Fexpenses into their savings when
OL,9,Fbuilding their deposit. More than a
OL,10,Ffifth (21%) borrowed more on their
OL,11,Fmortgage so they could keep savings
OL,12,Fback to fund improvements after moving
OL,13,Fin.
OL,15,FCarlo Pileggi, Nationwide's head of
OL,16,Fmortgage products, said: "For many
OL,17,Ffirst-time buyers, opting for a
OL,18,Fcheaper property that needs work is a
OL,19,Fdeliberate and savvy choice rather
OL,20,Fthan a compromise.
OL,26,@xD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
