OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778292208
OL,3,CSurvey reveals how first-time buyers
OL,4,Care achieving dream home on a budget
OL,6,F"By taking on a home requiring
OL,7,Frenovation, they are not only able to
OL,8,Fget onto the property ladder in the
OL,9,Flocation they want, but they can shape
OL,10,Fit to their own taste while adding to
OL,11,Fits value.
OL,13,F"Although there's a real enthusiasm
OL,14,Famongst first-time buyers to roll up
OL,15,Ftheir sleeves, our research suggests
OL,16,Fmany have had to undertake more work
OL,17,Fthan they initially intended. This is
OL,18,Fwhere planning and having the right
OL,19,Fsupport can make a real difference."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@dO]
