OL,3,CSurvey reveals how first-time buyers
OL,4,Care achieving dream home on a budget
OL,6,FNationwide commissioned Censuswide to
OL,7,Fsurvey 2,000 first-time buyers across
OL,8,Fthe UK in April.
OL,10,FHere are the percentages of first-time
OL,11,Fbuyers who were able to purchase a
OL,12,Fcheaper home because it needed
OL,13,Frenovation, according to Nationwide:
OL,15,FNorth East, 77%
OL,17,FLondon, 70%
OL,19,FEast of England, 69%
OL,21,FNorth West, 67%
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
